Package pathfinder.informed

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MazeProblem
    Specifies the Maze Grid pathfinding problem including the actions, transitions, goal test, and solution test.
    MazeState
    Maze Pathfinding representation of a given state, i.e., an occupiable position in the given maze.
    Pathfinder
    Maze Pathfinding algorithm that implements a basic, uninformed, breadth-first tree search.
    PathfinderTests
    Unit tests for Maze Pathfinder.
